---- MODULE Dekker ----
EXTENDS Integers, Sequences, FiniteSets

VARIABLES turn, wants

Init == /\ turn \in {0,1}
        /\ wants \in SUBSET {0,1}
        /\ turn = 0
        /\ wants = {}

Next == \/ /\ turn = 0
          /\ wants = {1}
          /\ turn' = 1
          /\ wants' = {}
        \/ /\ turn = 1
          /\ wants = {0}
          /\ turn' = 0
          /\ wants' = {}

Spec == Init /\ [][Next]_<<turn, wants>>

TypeOK == /\ turn \in {0,1}
          /\ wants \in SUBSET {0,1}

====
